  <description type="morphology">Plants 3–10 dm. Aerial flowering stems not fistulose, (1.5–)2–4 dm, glabrous. Leaves basal; blade 1–5 × 0.5–2 cm, tomentose abaxially, thinly floccose or glabrous adaxially, margins plane. Inflorescences cymose, 20–50 cm; branches glabrous. Involucres 2–5 per cluster, 3–5 mm, glabrous or sparsely pubescent. Flowers 2–3 mm; perianth white, rarely yellow, glabrous. 2n = 40.</description>
